<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu'n naupangte A hehpih,
 Lunggil hehpihnan A dim;
 Sun leh zanin A veng zinga,
 A Lalchutphah a patin.

[V2]
 Isu'n ei hehpih hi ka hei,
 Amah a maicha ka hi a;
 Isu'n ei hehpih ka kipak,
 Ama'n ei tatdawk ka hi.

[V3]
 2. Ka kipahna ziek nei dawt leh,
 Krista kei dinga thi chuh;
 Chun Bible inle ei hilh hi,
 &quot;Naupangte, hungun&quot; a ti.

[V4]
 3. Isu'n naupang ngetna A za'i,
 A Lalchutphah apatin;
 Hungun Amah chawian hitiu,
 Van-gam phaiphuleng haw tawh.</lyrics>
<title>JESUS LOVES THE LITTE CHILDREN</title>
<hymn_number>417</hymn_number>
</song>